  "rationale": "<p>Compute pv = (2x + 3)(x + 7) = 2x<sup>2</sup> + 17x + 21. Then &minus;3p = &minus;6x &minus; 9, and v = x + 7. Combine: 2x<sup>2</sup> + (17 &minus; 6 + 1)x + (21 &minus; 9 + 7) = 2x<sup>2</sup> + 12x + 19. Choice C is correct.</p>",
